dialogue.text: J: Oh nova, I had so much fun today! That shooting you were in, it was stressful for everyone. This was very much needed. Some time together.
J: I loved when we bought cinnamon rolls and got food at the mall...
J: or when we went to the supermarket and you pushed me around in the cart.
J: Oh yeah, baby! I can't forget the arcades! That shit was mad fun.
J: And now... we're taking a walk through busy ass Time Square. Today, has been the best.
J: I dunno man, like... it's gonna sound mad cringe but I don't care.
J: I REALLY love spending time with you. I know I tell you this all the time but you make me feel things I haven't felt before.
J: Sometimes i feel like I'm on top of the world when we're together. I actually feel safe. Here. With you.
J: Diablo. I've been hurt too many times in the past. It's cringe but I don't wanna lose this. I know that deep down, you wouldn't do anything to hurt me. I trust you.
N: I'm really glad you think that, Jasmine. Its.. heart warming to hear that, and I mean it.
J: Pump your brakes, my G. You talking now!? Damnn, now I know this shit is gonna be good, haha!
N: Yeah. I am. You say you trust me, right? Trust me when I say you be a total bitch sometimes...
J: H-huh? Sorry, these people be loud as hell around here. Whatcha say, babe?
N: You really have a raspy voice no one likes. You're way too loud and obnoxious, which must make it hard for people to be around you. I get happy when we both go home.
J: Are you deadass?? I KNOW you buggin' right now. Why.. why the hell are you being so damn mean for like-
N: I'ma be honest. I already had 5 girls behind your back. 6. My bad, forgot your sister. I kept you around for the status. Nice to know you feeling me tho.
J: AIN'T NO WAY! Imma deadass kill you! YOU KNOW I'M NOT DOING WELL MENTALLY. I TRUSTED YOU! ALL OF MY INSECURITIES!
J: After all that we've been through! I came out here to help YOU! SPEND TIME WITH YOU! FOR US! JUST FOR you to say...-
J: Dios.. mio.. no no no...
